=== Install mechanisms per node ===
  muddy     LaunchAgent user-scope gui/uid (active GUI session)
  lockwood  LaunchDaemon system-scope (Prometheus also)
  walter    LaunchDaemon system-scope (headless, no GUI session)
  otis      LaunchAgent user-scope (install script default)
  lomax     LaunchAgent user-scope (install script default)
  below     windows_exporter Windows service (MSI, auto-start)
  jimmy     systemd system unit (br3-node-exporter.service)

=== Firewall rules ===
  macOS nodes: ApplicationFirewall + pf anchor, LAN only (10.0.1.0/24)
  jimmy      : ufw allow from 10.0.1.0/24 to any port 9100
  below      : netsh advfirewall rule TCP 9182 remoteip=10.0.1.0/24
